id: exec_profiles
type: custom
order: after champions
title: Executive Profiles
slide_type: custom
data_tools: [customer_people, customer_kei]
customers: all

prompt: |
  Show a profile card for each known executive at this customer. Include
  their name, title, last login date, Kei usage, and whether they attended
  the most recent QBR (if that data is available from Salesforce).

  If Salesforce contact data is available, pull executive titles and contact
  info from there rather than Pendo roles — Pendo roles are self-reported
  and often inaccurate for executives. Cross-reference: if Salesforce shows
  a VP who has never appeared in Pendo, flag that as a gap.

  This slide helps the CSM prepare for executive conversations by knowing
  exactly who is engaged and who needs outreach.
